WEBVTT

00:00:20.059 --> 00:00:21.352
vil epes zogn

00:00:24.312 --> 00:00:29.537
her ZANZER, yetst hostu gezogt az du bist arayn mit di armey in DRESDEN arayn.

00:00:29.661 --> 00:00:31.275
vos hot pasirt dortn?

00:00:31.973 --> 00:00:34.903
ikh vel aykh zogn, ⟨iz⟩ di militer

00:00:36.360 --> 00:00:41.290
iz geven ⟨farn ORDER⟩, hot yeder gezogt vos vet er tun

00:00:41.290 --> 00:00:43.650
az er vet ibergeyn di daytshishe grenets.

00:00:43.701 --> 00:00:46.070
yeder hot gevolt hargenen.

00:00:46.070 --> 00:00:48.380
yeder hot gevolt nekome nemen.

00:00:49.067 --> 00:00:50.529
m'hot, m'hot genumen.

00:00:50.940 --> 00:00:51.913
vi nokh?

00:00:52.122 --> 00:00:56.227
vi m'hot gemegt. nokh dem iz geven a bafel fun STALINen

00:00:56.227 --> 00:00:58.342
far MARODYORSTVO shisn

00:00:59.361 --> 00:01:01.143
veyst vos MARODYORSTVO heyst?

00:01:00.778 --> 00:01:01.514
NO

00:01:01.926 --> 00:01:02.814
f-

00:01:03.192 --> 00:01:06.274
f- farbrekherishe zakhn. banditizm.

00:01:06.448 --> 00:01:10.104
hargenen, mentshn hargenen, froyen har- azoy ⟨vi⟩ der daytsh hot getun.

00:01:10.144 --> 00:01:12.298
iz geven a bafel fun STALIN

00:01:12.456 --> 00:01:14.880
az far di zakhn, ver s'vet tun vet men hargenen.

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:20.178
yetst azoyne zakhn zogn, emetser zol dos hern

00:01:20.472 --> 00:01:22.558
vos mir flegn tun ken ikh nisht.

00:01:23.678 --> 00:01:25.039
dir ken ikh dertseyln.

00:01:26.142 --> 00:01:27.013
nor nisht do.

00:01:27.846 --> 00:01:29.105
kh'hob nokh kinder.

00:01:29.550 --> 00:01:31.164
az du vilst nisht

00:01:31.744 --> 00:01:33.037
me meg nisht, meyn ikh.

00:01:35.727 --> 00:01:36.750
tsvishn undz

00:01:38.173 --> 00:01:38.960
yo.

00:01:40.148 --> 00:01:42.471
az du vilst ken men dos haltn

00:01:42.493 --> 00:01:43.347
far

00:01:43.219 --> 00:01:44.259
mir veln redn.

00:01:43.928 --> 00:01:44.631
OKAY.

00:01:46.054 --> 00:01:48.106
in zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:01:51.268 --> 00:01:53.287
azoy september, oktober

00:01:54.711 --> 00:01:57.236
iz kinder vos zenen geven frayvilik

00:01:57.394 --> 00:02:00.256
un kinder vos, vos zey hobn

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:03.379
di yorn nisht tsugan tsum militer hot men opgelozt

00:02:05.325 --> 00:02:06.466
fun militer.

00:02:07.384 --> 00:02:08.815
hot men der mayor

00:02:08.815 --> 00:02:09.892
BURSHTEYN

00:02:10.506 --> 00:02:12.238
vos er hot geratevet

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:13.976
in BERLIN

00:02:15.552 --> 00:02:16.778
a S.S.

00:02:17.408 --> 00:02:20.945
in akhtn tsi in nayntn may iz aroys.

00:02:22.453 --> 00:02:24.016
ikh hob getrogn

00:02:24.394 --> 00:02:25.716
a ⟨PARABEL⟩ i-

00:02:25.716 --> 00:02:26.835
in di shtivl

00:02:27.010 --> 00:02:28.016
⟨in⟩ do.

00:02:29.625 --> 00:02:32.685
tsi er hot im gevolt shisn tsi er hot gevolt aropnemen fun im

00:02:32.685 --> 00:02:33.675
di antsugn

00:02:34.182 --> 00:02:36.926
nor ikh hob mit eyn shis avekgeleygt im

00:02:37.033 --> 00:02:38.208
di S.S.?

00:02:37.725 --> 00:02:38.630
dem S.S.

00:02:40.459 --> 00:02:43.963
der mayor hot mir geratevet. ikh hob im geratevet.

00:02:45.302 --> 00:02:47.101
dos iz geven a mentsh fun mentshn

00:02:48.492 --> 00:02:51.726
mit a goldn harts, un aleyn iz er geven a dokter.

00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:56.669
dos iz nor funem himl kenen kumen azoyne mentshn.

00:02:57.857 --> 00:02:59.364
normal ven nisht er

00:02:59.364 --> 00:03:00.483
efsher volt ikh

00:03:00.574 --> 00:03:02.762
a a- andere rikhtung genumen.

00:03:02.852 --> 00:03:06.376
efsher volt ikh nisht geven azoy bisl tsivilizirt vayl ikh bin geven

00:03:06.376 --> 00:03:07.301
vild.

00:03:08.843 --> 00:03:10.046
er hot mir oysge⟨UNK⟩.

00:03:10.046 --> 00:03:12.886
nor oplozn, er iz avekgeforn keyn TASHKENT.

00:03:13.905 --> 00:03:15.721
mer hob ikh nisht gehert fun im.

00:03:17.128 --> 00:03:19.197
nor er hot mir ibergegebn a andern

00:03:20.115 --> 00:03:21.290
in MORSHYN

00:03:22.022 --> 00:03:23.315
in Stri

00:03:23.457 --> 00:03:24.497
mayor

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:25.813
GOLDHEFTER

00:03:26.359 --> 00:03:27.483
ISAK.

00:03:28.317 --> 00:03:31.511
oykh geven a dokter, zayner a bakanter farshtendlekh

00:03:31.511 --> 00:03:33.131
ikh zol nisht farfaln vern

00:03:33.131 --> 00:03:34.841
hot er mir ibergegebn im.

00:03:38.003 --> 00:03:39.279
er hot gehat

00:03:40.348 --> 00:03:42.164
tsvey zin un a tokhter.

00:03:42.863 --> 00:03:44.730
zeks un fertsikster yor

00:03:45.107 --> 00:03:47.415
iz geven a shreklekher yor a hunger

00:03:47.415 --> 00:03:48.341
in Rusland.

00:03:48.634 --> 00:03:50.790
ikh hob gehat dem ganeydn dortn.

00:03:51.115 --> 00:03:53.353
dort iz geven gefangene daytshn.

00:03:53.967 --> 00:03:56.171
a lager fun gefangene daytshn.

00:03:56.211 --> 00:03:58.837
ikh bin arayngefaln in mayn

00:03:59.991 --> 00:04:01.014
arbet.

00:04:05.492 --> 00:04:07.173
er hot mir f- gezogt.

00:04:07.635 --> 00:04:09.283
az ikh tor gornisht tun

00:04:10.757 --> 00:04:12.354
ikh zol zikh firn mentshlekh

00:04:14.318 --> 00:04:15.915
vayl di milkhome iz geendikt.

00:04:19.649 --> 00:04:21.347
ikh hob mayn arbet gut getun.

00:04:21.962 --> 00:04:23.745
vu iz geven dos lager?

00:04:23.785 --> 00:04:25.382
der lager iz geven in Stri.

00:04:26.130 --> 00:04:27.339
dort iz geven

00:04:27.666 --> 00:04:29.786
zey hobn geboyt dortn di daytshn

00:04:30.130 --> 00:04:31.845
un dos iz geven a shpitol

00:04:32.340 --> 00:04:33.971
fun gefangene daytshn.

00:04:35.749 --> 00:04:38.691
f- fun, fun, fun plen

00:04:38.691 --> 00:04:39.911
vos m'hot genumen.

00:04:40.322 --> 00:04:42.290
dort hobn zey durkhgegan

00:04:42.516 --> 00:04:45.041
dort ver, ver se fleg shtarbn

00:04:45.807 --> 00:04:47.522
iz fleg men oyfmakhn

00:04:47.629 --> 00:04:48.905
a AUTOPSIYA makhn.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.964
ikh fleg makhn di AUTOPSIYA.

00:04:52.523 --> 00:04:55.014
der dokter fleg mir zogn vu ikh darf hakn

00:04:55.780 --> 00:04:57.208
fleg ikh hakn.

00:04:56.083 --> 00:04:58.389
far vos hobn zey gemakht a AUTOPSIYA?

00:04:58.497 --> 00:05:01.461
ikh veys nisht. far vos er iz geshtorbn, m'hot gedarft bashraybn

00:05:01.737 --> 00:05:03.081
m'hot gedarft zogn

00:05:03.340 --> 00:05:05.477
iz fleg ikh shnaydn di kep

00:05:06.765 --> 00:05:09.120
mit a zeg oyfmakhn.

00:05:09.610 --> 00:05:10.890
ikh fleg di ale

00:05:10.900 --> 00:05:12.581
geven a guter arbetor

00:05:13.262 --> 00:05:14.876
mitn shenstn fargenign.

00:05:15.203 --> 00:05:17.576
kh'hob gehat hanoe. ikh fleg afile esn oykhet.

00:05:17.869 --> 00:05:19.010
s'hot mikh nisht geshtert.

00:05:20.788 --> 00:05:22.841
s'iz geven a sakh S.S. dortn?

00:05:22.594 --> 00:05:23.685
ikh veys nisht.

00:05:25.497 --> 00:05:26.638
ikh veys nisht

00:05:26.914 --> 00:05:31.194
vos iz geven dortn veys ikh nisht, nor zey hobn gearbet. m'hot zey gut badint.

00:05:31.538 --> 00:05:33.708
nor ⟨az zey⟩ geshtorbn, m'hot UNK gema-

00:05:33.708 --> 00:05:35.788
geven a dokter KALDERASH

00:05:37.208 --> 00:05:38.748
KALDERASH a dokter

00:05:38.748 --> 00:05:42.984
vos er hot geven zeyer bafraynt mit mir. er hot mir lib gehat

00:05:42.984 --> 00:05:44.441
un ikh fleg im helfn.

00:05:44.903 --> 00:05:46.230
vayter veln mir shvaygn.

00:05:46.843 --> 00:05:48.372
iz

00:05:48.666 --> 00:05:52.254
der lager iz geven in zeks un fertsikstn yor

00:05:52.362 --> 00:05:58.110
un me fleg zey oplozn langzam ver s'hot gut gearbet, fleg men oplozn keyn DEUTSCHLAND. me fleg zey ontun.

00:05:57.070 --> 00:05:59.173
tsuriktsushikn nokh DEUTSCHLAND.

00:05:58.640 --> 00:06:00.506
yo. me fleg zey ontun.

00:06:00.732 --> 00:06:02.312
FREUNDLICH, zeyer FREUNDLICH

00:06:02.655 --> 00:06:04.421
fleg men zey avekshikn keyn DEUTSCHLAND.

00:06:05.153 --> 00:06:07.560
un ikh hob dort gearbet bizn

00:06:08.123 --> 00:06:10.074
bizn akht un fertsikstn yor.

00:06:10.401 --> 00:06:11.056
lo-

00:06:11.056 --> 00:06:12.166
mit dem

00:06:12.763 --> 00:06:15.575
hot mir geshikt fun, fun di partey

00:06:15.987 --> 00:06:16.861
helfn

00:06:16.861 --> 00:06:19.474
kemfn kegn di ukraynishe banditn.

00:06:21.150 --> 00:06:22.494
dos hot geheysn

00:06:22.737 --> 00:06:26.545
zey hobn gezogt az zey viln fray Ukraine

00:06:26.955 --> 00:06:30.054
un zey hobn keyn yidn nisht getshepet

00:06:30.617 --> 00:06:34.796
partey mentshn, komunistn, dos, yents. a terets hobn zey gedarft hobn.

00:06:35.578 --> 00:06:38.744
nor ikh bin geven der meyvn oyf zey.

00:06:39.966 --> 00:06:42.035
m'hot mir gerufn frayvilik

00:06:42.193 --> 00:06:43.616
ven ikh zog zikh op

00:06:43.616 --> 00:06:44.685
iz nisht gut

00:06:45.231 --> 00:06:47.537
nor ikh bin take gan frayvilik.

00:06:48.100 --> 00:06:50.304
UNK dem kop oykh avekleygn

00:06:52.588 --> 00:06:55.282
nor ikh bin gan mitn shenstn fargenign.

00:06:57.313 --> 00:06:58.623
kh'hob tsvey yor

00:06:58.782 --> 00:07:00.041
in di velder

00:07:00.165 --> 00:07:01.813
gekemft kegn zey.

00:07:02.207 --> 00:07:03.450
d'host gefunen?

00:07:03.658 --> 00:07:06.777
kh'hob a sakh gefunen. dos vos ikh hob gefunen, ander hobn nisht gekent gefinen.

00:07:06.777 --> 00:07:08.884
fun mir iz geven shver zikh tsu farshtekn.

00:07:09.075 --> 00:07:10.149
zeyer shver.

00:07:12.349 --> 00:07:15.954
ikh bin geven a mentsh, a oysgelernter mentsh

00:07:16.500 --> 00:07:19.430
un fun mir iz geven sh- zeyer shlekht avektsugeyn.

00:07:20.078 --> 00:07:22.502
⟨in akht⟩ hob ikh gezen s- halt shmol

00:07:22.828 --> 00:07:25.859
dos toyg nisht. ikh ken farnikhtn vern

00:07:26.473 --> 00:07:28.141
iz bin ikh gegan.

00:07:28.141 --> 00:07:34.939
ikh hob gedarft geyn in militer. m'hot mir nisht gerufn. kh'hob gedarft say vi geyn. akht un fertsikstn yor iz mayn yor tsugegan. bin gevorn nayntsn yor

00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:37.217
hot mir genumen in militer

00:07:38.202 --> 00:07:42.482
un ikh hob gedint in VLADIMIR VOLINSK, Ukraine.

00:07:44.142 --> 00:07:45.806
vi azoy ikh bin shoyn geven

00:07:45.829 --> 00:07:49.940
oysgelernt mit alemen, hot mir geshikt in a shule

00:07:50.318 --> 00:07:51.825
POLKOVAYA SHKOLA

00:07:51.825 --> 00:07:52.399
do-

00:07:52.399 --> 00:07:54.024
oyf unterofitsern.

00:07:55.701 --> 00:07:57.855
ikh hob gelernt in di POLKOVAYA SHKOLA

00:07:58.097 --> 00:08:02.563
un ikh hob gevust az nokh di militer darf ikh zikh lebn. keyn mame hob ikh nisht

00:08:03.767 --> 00:08:06.883
hob ikh gezogt ikh vil vayter lernen. mir hot men nokh gegebn.

00:08:07.918 --> 00:08:10.426
hot men mir geshikt in a shule fun mekhanik.

00:08:11.698 --> 00:08:14.257
hob ikh gelernt a halb yor mekhanik

00:08:14.517 --> 00:08:16.300
un aleyn bin ikh geven

00:08:16.423 --> 00:08:19.555
fun di MINOMYOTn. veyst vos MINOMYOTN iz?

00:08:20.153 --> 00:08:22.678
dos iz mines vos me shtelt arayn

00:08:23.022 --> 00:08:24.096
un zey shisn.

00:08:24.827 --> 00:08:26.576
ikh bin geven der

00:08:26.700 --> 00:08:28.466
v- vos hob ongefirt.

00:08:29.974 --> 00:08:31.852
dort hob ikh gelernt als mekhanik

00:08:31.852 --> 00:08:36.020
un ikh ho- un ikh hob shpeter in di shule gegebn LESSON fun elektrye

00:08:36.020 --> 00:08:37.380
AUTO elektrye.

00:08:37.669 --> 00:08:39.705
ikh bin geven a NACHAL'NIK

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:42.399
fun, fun reparirn

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:44.660
vogns. STUDEBAKER

00:08:44.660 --> 00:08:48.918
G.M.C. ale amerikanishe vogns vos iz geven oyf militer

00:08:49.060 --> 00:08:50.454
fleg ikh onfirn.

00:08:51.591 --> 00:08:52.817
un ikh hob

00:08:52.823 --> 00:08:56.783
kh'hob gedint, kh'bin geven tsufridn mitn dinst.

00:08:56.783 --> 00:08:58.133
vu zol ikh geyn?

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:00.010
esn trinken hob ikh.

00:09:00.010 --> 00:09:01.820
di lage iz geven zeyer shver dortn

00:09:01.820 --> 00:09:03.170
un ikh hob gemuzt dinen

00:09:03.170 --> 00:09:04.764
vayl mayn yor iz tsugekumen.

00:09:05.192 --> 00:09:07.346
in eyn un fuftsikstn yor

00:09:07.842 --> 00:09:10.502
hob ikh zikh demobilizirt fun di militer

00:09:11.858 --> 00:09:14.310
m'hot mir opgelozt di tsayt, tsvey

00:09:14.310 --> 00:09:16.600
tsvey yor un akht monatn hob ikh getun.

00:09:17.983 --> 00:09:20.761
iz geven, nokh a mol kumt zi tsu mir

00:09:22.270 --> 00:09:24.441
a soldat fun KISHINYOV

00:09:25.020 --> 00:09:26.566
vos er iz geven a shuster.

00:09:26.742 --> 00:09:28.406
vu kumt er arayn

00:09:28.783 --> 00:09:29.958
in mekhanik?

00:09:30.707 --> 00:09:32.113
hot er mir gebetn

00:09:32.113 --> 00:09:35.611
oyb ikh ken, zol im dortn ⟨angazhirn⟩, dortn UNK

00:09:35.837 --> 00:09:37.265
laykhter arbet

00:09:39.145 --> 00:09:42.531
hob ikh im gezogt "vos kenstu?" "dir vel ikh zogn dem emes. ikh bin a shuster."

00:09:43.937 --> 00:09:45.910
hob ikh im genumen ineveynik.

00:09:45.910 --> 00:09:47.400
kh'hob im tsugelernt

00:09:47.835 --> 00:09:51.254
vos er darf tun. er fleg di reder aropnemen, dos

00:09:51.717 --> 00:09:55.120
un ikh hob gezogt dem ofitser, er iz a guter mekhanik

00:09:55.615 --> 00:09:57.111
un zol er blaybn do.

00:09:57.353 --> 00:09:59.524
hob ikh im oysgedreyt fun shvere

00:09:59.884 --> 00:10:01.548
militerishe zakhn.

00:10:03.445 --> 00:10:05.515
ven ikh bin avek in militer, hot er

00:10:05.515 --> 00:10:07.535
gedarft nokh a, a yor dinen

00:10:08.305 --> 00:10:09.176
blaybn

00:10:09.402 --> 00:10:11.421
hot er mir gezogt "for tsu mir."

00:10:11.848 --> 00:10:14.036
ikh hob keyn mol nisht gevolt zayn aleyn.

00:10:15.223 --> 00:10:16.820
kh'hob gevolt zayn tsvishn mentshn.

00:10:19.662 --> 00:10:21.225
bin gekumen keyn Keshenev

00:10:21.433 --> 00:10:22.721
tsu zayn muter

00:10:22.721 --> 00:10:25.286
hot zi gehat a shvester, un punkt zayn shvester

00:10:25.286 --> 00:10:27.215
oyf mayn mazl hot khasene gehat.

00:10:27.913 --> 00:10:29.189
un der man

00:10:30.006 --> 00:10:31.518
er iz yetst in Yisroel

00:10:31.812 --> 00:10:33.358
hot nisht gehat keyn fakh.

00:10:35.119 --> 00:10:37.029
ikh bin gan arbetn

00:10:37.029 --> 00:10:38.299
bay di FLUGZEUGEN

00:10:38.299 --> 00:10:39.929
alts mekhanik fun AUTOS.

00:10:39.984 --> 00:10:41.255
kh'hob gut fardint.

00:10:41.413 --> 00:10:42.689
un ikh hob gut

00:10:43.219 --> 00:10:45.173
gekent gesheftn makhn in Rusland.

00:10:45.173 --> 00:10:47.516
kh'hob gehat a ⟨tsutret⟩ umedum, vayl

00:10:47.590 --> 00:10:52.258
ikh bin geven mit ofitsern vos zenen avekgan fun militer. kh'hob gehat kontaktn groyse

00:10:52.703 --> 00:10:55.785
hob ikh gezogt "SYOMA, du lern a fakh

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:57.287
un ikh'l oyshaltn."

00:10:59.098 --> 00:11:00.256
hot der

00:11:00.651 --> 00:11:02.687
man gelernt alts toker.

00:11:02.710 --> 00:11:04.039
veys vos toker iz?

00:11:04.039 --> 00:11:06.736
ayzn shnaydn ⟨⟩ farshidene zakhn

00:11:08.869 --> 00:11:12.238
un ikh bin geven bay zey etlekhe yor.

00:11:12.582 --> 00:11:14.398
kh'hob oysgehaltn di gantse familye.

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:16.102
kh'hob gearbet oyf zey

00:11:16.243 --> 00:11:19.409
un zeyer voyle mentshn, AVERBUKH SYOMA.

00:11:19.872 --> 00:11:23.241
ven er iz gekumen keyn Yisroel, iz er gevorn a raykher mentsh.

00:11:23.449 --> 00:11:25.400
er iz gan arbetn bay di UNK.

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:27.459
a spetsyalist iz er geven a guter

00:11:27.904 --> 00:11:31.307
yetst az ikh kum keyn Yisroel, veyst er vos tsu tun mit mir.

00:11:33.253 --> 00:11:35.086
hob ikh oyfgeshtelt oyf di fis im.

00:11:37.928 --> 00:11:41.195
un, un nokh dem hob ikh ge- hob ikh gearbet

00:11:42.298 --> 00:11:47.118
kh'hob gefirt a minister fun AU- fun transport fun MOLDAVIA

00:11:47.378 --> 00:11:50.106
hob ikh bakumen groys ge- bakantshaft

00:11:50.668 --> 00:11:53.041
un ikh fleg rays- ikh fleg helfn yidn.

00:11:53.132 --> 00:11:56.006
der iz arayngefaln mit dem, der mit dem

00:11:56.006 --> 00:11:58.880
un ikh bin gevorn a, ⟨oyf zey⟩ a rebe bay zey.

00:11:59.072 --> 00:12:03.436
oyf der arbet fleg ikh tsunoyfnemen gelt, ver yesoymim, ver dos, ver yents.

00:12:03.578 --> 00:12:04.258
kh'hob

00:12:04.258 --> 00:12:05.481
kh'hob lib gehat

00:12:05.481 --> 00:12:07.351
tun toyves hob ikh lib gehat.

00:12:08.927 --> 00:12:09.933
un

00:12:10.345 --> 00:12:12.566
hostu gegat familye in Rusland?

00:12:12.437 --> 00:12:13.610
keynem nisht.

00:12:13.568 --> 00:12:17.106
nisht a kuzin, nisht a k- a kuzine, a k- kuzin

00:12:13.704 --> 00:12:14.984
far dem hob ikh gez-

00:12:16.757 --> 00:12:20.074
ikh hob, ikh hob gekent, ikh hob gekent di ma- di mume

00:12:20.074 --> 00:12:21.844
vos zi hot gezitsn oyf tsvey benklekh.

00:12:21.844 --> 00:12:23.450
kh'hob fargesn tsu zogn.

00:12:23.895 --> 00:12:25.917
mayn mame iz geven

00:12:25.917 --> 00:12:27.550
nisht dik, azoy vi du.

00:12:27.591 --> 00:12:31.685
zi iz gefaln un di geto. zi hot gornisht gekent tun. un di mume iz gevorn gezunt.

00:12:31.776 --> 00:12:33.035
zi iz gevorn moger

00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:35.718
un zi iz geven di gantse arbetorin.

00:12:37.277 --> 00:12:39.274
dos vil zogn, di dike mentshn

00:12:39.274 --> 00:12:40.697
darfn geyn in lager

00:12:42.070 --> 00:12:43.431
⟨un veln⟩ kumen tsurik.

00:12:43.605 --> 00:12:45.067
gevorn a gezunter mentsh.

00:12:45.107 --> 00:12:48.442
vi zey geyen un loyfn un tun. vu zi iz umgekumen veys ikh nisht.

00:12:48.448 --> 00:12:52.374
SO bistu geblibn aleyn, eyn eyntsiker, on a familye.

00:12:52.093 --> 00:12:56.272
eyn, eyn, eyntsiker. ikh hob yetst ⟨in⟩ roytn kreyts

00:12:56.329 --> 00:12:58.786
ayngeshribn, mayn foter

00:12:58.962 --> 00:13:00.323
hot gehat a bruder.

00:13:01.037 --> 00:13:04.282
mir flegn bakumen bilder, ikh gedenk vi haynt, mit a bord

00:13:04.282 --> 00:13:05.658
a shoykhet dakht zikh.

00:13:05.658 --> 00:13:06.988
er hot gehat kinder.

00:13:08.918 --> 00:13:09.755
un

00:13:09.880 --> 00:13:11.072
ikh meyn

00:13:11.331 --> 00:13:15.421
az er hot getrakht tsu forn keyn Amerike, mayn bru- mayn foter

00:13:15.421 --> 00:13:17.811
nor di krig iz oysgebrokhn.

00:13:18.199 --> 00:13:19.509
hob ikh getrakht

00:13:20.798 --> 00:13:24.454
Amerike. Amerike iz ⟨dokh⟩ nisht keyn dorf, nisht LIBANOVKA.

00:13:25.050 --> 00:13:27.018
vu gefint men a nodl in hey?

00:13:28.375 --> 00:13:30.160
vu zol ikh shraybn? umzist.

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:32.233
ikh vey- ikh veys nisht vi azoy er heyst afile

00:13:32.948 --> 00:13:37.009
hob ikh yetst ayngefilt a ankete az emetser vet kukn, vet er lakhn.

00:13:37.150 --> 00:13:38.454
hob ongeshribn

00:13:38.454 --> 00:13:45.108
az mayn foter hot geheysn azoy un azoy. er hot gehat a bruder in Amerike. vi azoy er heyst veys ikh nisht. vi alt veys ikh nisht.

00:13:45.233 --> 00:13:49.933
ikh zukh zayne kinder, ikh zol bakumen a foto khotsh fun mayn familye

00:13:49.933 --> 00:13:52.803
vayl ale, ikh veys, m'hot geshikt a sakh fotos.

00:13:53.299 --> 00:13:54.182
nor vi

00:13:54.182 --> 00:13:55.354
shraybt er zikh

00:13:55.354 --> 00:13:59.182
Tsantser in IVRIT tsi in yidish ⟨khapt⟩ zikh tsvey tsadikn.

00:13:59.273 --> 00:14:00.954
ken men gefinen nokh efsher.

00:14:00.994 --> 00:14:03.488
do, g- ikh bin shoyn gevorn Z.

00:14:03.488 --> 00:14:06.523
ZANZER. ikh bin geven CANCER, der C. in Poyln

00:14:09.094 --> 00:14:11.349
efsher shraybt men ⟨zikh dokh⟩ S.

00:14:13.279 --> 00:14:14.263
veys ikh nisht.

00:14:14.263 --> 00:14:18.507
der royter kreyts hot gezogt, a, a neger, a simpatisher mentsh azoy

00:14:18.507 --> 00:14:20.883
hot er UNK ⟨tsu⟩ tun ale meglekhkeytn.

00:14:21.092 --> 00:14:22.959
tsu mir kumen ale gute mentshn.

00:14:23.488 --> 00:14:25.895
er hot nisht umzist der, der foter gedavnt.

00:14:26.323 --> 00:14:28.395
er iz a, er zol zukhn.

00:14:28.395 --> 00:14:31.261
vet er gefinen, zol zayn gliklekh ⟨tsi⟩ er nisht gefinen

00:14:32.466 --> 00:14:37.320
un ven hostu khasene gegat? ven hostu gekent dayn froy?

00:14:35.588 --> 00:14:37.044
in mar-

00:14:37.044 --> 00:14:40.019
in mar- mart nayn un fuftsik.

00:14:39.925 --> 00:14:42.180
ven hostu bakent dayn froy? vi nokh?

00:14:44.211 --> 00:14:45.453
oykh in a tsore.

00:14:45.882 --> 00:14:47.243
ir foter

00:14:47.383 --> 00:14:48.997
iz gezitsn in tfise.

00:14:50.472 --> 00:14:52.181
er hot gemakht gesheftn

00:14:52.181 --> 00:14:53.835
in Rusland iz dos bakant.

00:14:53.835 --> 00:14:55.157
s'iz nisht keyn bushe

00:14:55.905 --> 00:14:58.362
un er iz arayngefaln bay dem UNK tsu elef yor.

00:14:59.365 --> 00:15:00.315
ven

00:15:00.315 --> 00:15:02.345
zi volt mir gekent friert

00:15:02.824 --> 00:15:04.218
volt es nisht pasirt.

00:15:05.895 --> 00:15:09.163
a tokhter zogt a mol tsu di mame, "mame, s'iz tsu shpet."

00:15:11.329 --> 00:15:12.656
s'iz geven tsu shpet.

00:15:12.679 --> 00:15:16.352
ikh hob khasene gehat, zey hobn gornisht gehat, un ikh bin geven der oysher.

00:15:16.729 --> 00:15:18.933
ikh hob genumen di gantse familye oyf zikh.

00:15:20.442 --> 00:15:21.820
vi heyst dayn froy?

00:15:21.842 --> 00:15:22.680
NELLY.

00:15:22.821 --> 00:15:24.367
un fun di heym?

00:15:23.340 --> 00:15:24.536
LANDSMAN.

00:15:24.677 --> 00:15:27.635
zi hot tsvey feters in Yisroel.

00:15:27.635 --> 00:15:31.455
er hot gearbet in SHIN BET meyn ikh, tsi in POLICE. er iz yetst

00:15:31.545 --> 00:15:32.788
oyf pensye.

00:15:33.098 --> 00:15:34.746
e- er iz UNK

00:15:34.920 --> 00:15:36.669
er hot yetst farloyrn a tokhter.

00:15:38.127 --> 00:15:40.047
eyn feter iz in P-

00:15:40.047 --> 00:15:43.877
fun UNK SOCHNUT gearbet, iz er UNK ⟨mit im⟩ in TEL AVIV

00:15:44.742 --> 00:15:48.634
un eyn mume iz in HAIFA.

00:15:49.787 --> 00:15:52.261
mir iz gut, bin a yosem. ikh hob keynem nisht.

00:15:53.230 --> 00:15:54.700
ikh bin mekane mentshn.

00:15:54.700 --> 00:16:00.240
⟨u- un hob ikh⟩ ikh has afile mentshn vos m'hot familye un me krigt zikh tsvishn zikh. dos ken ikh nisht fartrogn.

00:16:03.051 --> 00:16:07.095
SO ven bist avekgeforn, ven bist aroysgeforn fun Rusland?

00:16:07.067 --> 00:16:08.917
in tsvey un zibetsikstn yor may.

00:16:08.772 --> 00:16:09.846
far vos?

00:16:10.797 --> 00:16:13.845
far vos? ikh hob dos gantse lebn gekholemt in dem.

00:16:13.986 --> 00:16:16.005
nor mir iz geven shver aroystsuforn.

00:16:16.467 --> 00:16:20.758
kh'hob gekent forn keyn Poyln hob ikh gekent forn, friert nokh.

00:16:20.758 --> 00:16:25.657
nor ikh hob genumen in militer dos shverung

00:16:26.035 --> 00:16:29.811
un m- az me geyt in militer shteyt men bay di fon

00:16:29.811 --> 00:16:31.161
un me zogt

00:16:31.161 --> 00:16:33.521
az "ikh Tsantser

00:16:33.679 --> 00:16:35.428
JAN" hob ikh geheysn

00:16:35.721 --> 00:16:36.772
"shver ikh

00:16:36.772 --> 00:16:41.115
vel zayn getray Rusland un alemen," hob ikh farloyrn di poylishe birgershaft.

00:16:41.762 --> 00:16:43.646
bin ikh gevorn a rusisher birger.

00:16:43.973 --> 00:16:45.384
hob ikh nisht gekent forn.

00:16:46.268 --> 00:16:48.306
in tsvey un zibetsikstn yor

00:16:48.306 --> 00:16:50.295
mir hobn gelebt zeyer sheyn in Rusland.

00:16:51.567 --> 00:16:54.885
kh'hob gehat ales. kh'hob afile moyre gehat far mayn gelt

00:16:56.815 --> 00:16:59.003
hot der froy take nisht gevolt forn.

00:17:01.455 --> 00:17:02.861
hob ikh gezogt

00:17:02.861 --> 00:17:04.757
mayn foter hot gemakht a feler.

00:17:05.252 --> 00:17:06.489
er ⟨hot⟩ nisht geforn

00:17:06.489 --> 00:17:07.540
vel ikh forn.

00:17:08.914 --> 00:17:10.916
hob ikh tsebrokhn dos gantse lebn

00:17:12.593 --> 00:17:15.388
un ikh hob genumen a groysn bagazh

00:17:17.013 --> 00:17:18.239
un

00:17:18.313 --> 00:17:21.614
un im, un Khaim, hob ikh gezogt, er fort keyn Moskve.

00:17:21.722 --> 00:17:23.910
ven ikh zog im az er fort keyn Yisroel

00:17:23.933 --> 00:17:26.810
⟨iz di⟩ katastrofe. demolst iz nokh, geven shver demolst.

00:17:26.810 --> 00:17:28.027
m'hot gemuzt shvaygn.

00:17:28.101 --> 00:17:30.272
dos iz dayn zun, du redst derfun?

00:17:30.126 --> 00:17:33.280
dos, er iz geven alt akht yor, dos akhte yor.

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:36.770
vi ken men zogn er fort, az Yisroel iz geven a soyne kegn

00:17:36.770 --> 00:17:39.010
az Rusland iz geven a soyne kegn Yisroel.

00:17:39.694 --> 00:17:40.886
un ikh hob gegebn

00:17:41.517 --> 00:17:44.277
fir toyznt rubl in N.K.V.D.

00:17:44.277 --> 00:17:46.187
me zol mir nisht haltn.

00:17:48.013 --> 00:17:50.251
vifl kinder hostu gegat in di tsayt?

00:17:50.730 --> 00:17:53.609
Kh- Khaim un ALEKSANDER, beyde kinder, zeks un akht.

00:17:54.493 --> 00:17:56.141
hob ikh gezogt azoy.

00:17:57.700 --> 00:17:59.398
"vi azoy se nit iz

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:01.018
LENIN hot gezogt

00:18:01.075 --> 00:18:04.731
haynt darf men makhn di revolutsye. morgn vet zayn shpet."

00:18:04.939 --> 00:18:07.231
hot er gut getun tsi nit veys ikh nisht.

00:18:07.231 --> 00:18:10.175
me zet az nisht. ikh hob gezogt "haynt

00:18:10.175 --> 00:18:13.927
morgn." di kinder vern greser ⟨veln mir⟩ gornisht makhn fun zey.

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:21.049
hob ikh ales likvidirt un bin geforn.

00:18:22.624 --> 00:18:24.609
in Yisroel iz geven nisht laykht.

00:18:25.341 --> 00:18:26.735
zeyer shver.

00:18:27.417 --> 00:18:29.025
laykhter iz dem

00:18:29.025 --> 00:18:31.427
vos hot gehat a shver lebn in Rusland.

00:18:31.922 --> 00:18:33.974
der vos hot gehat a gut lebn

00:18:34.302 --> 00:18:35.595
iz oyf tsores.

00:18:36.023 --> 00:18:38.374
nor vos zhe, ikh bin gevoynt. mayn froy

00:18:38.374 --> 00:18:39.392
iz shvakher.

00:18:39.752 --> 00:18:42.615
zi hot gehat in Rusland a operatsye

00:18:42.857 --> 00:18:44.235
oyfn haldz.

00:18:45.372 --> 00:18:46.952
UNK

00:18:47.818 --> 00:18:49.212
dos vert geshvoln.

00:18:49.590 --> 00:18:50.849
in Yisroel

00:18:51.092 --> 00:18:52.874
iz zi gevorn azoy krank

00:18:53.016 --> 00:18:55.760
az ikh hob gemeynt az mayne kinder vern yesoymim.

00:18:56.205 --> 00:18:58.055
dos hob ikh nisht gevolt tsulozn.

00:18:58.973 --> 00:19:00.286
ikh bin geven a yosem

00:19:00.286 --> 00:19:01.245
un di kinder.

00:19:01.842 --> 00:19:04.418
fun Yisroel iz nisht laykht aroystsuforn.

00:19:05.233 --> 00:19:06.982
m'hot gedarft batsoln gelt.

00:19:09.908 --> 00:19:11.961
ikh hob zikh bakant

00:19:12.186 --> 00:19:17.782
in, in fun, fun England mit rav SEGAL.

00:19:19.915 --> 00:19:21.945
er hot mir gegebn a eytse

00:19:21.945 --> 00:19:24.205
az in Antverpn iz a yidishe shtot

00:19:24.205 --> 00:19:26.685
oyb ir vilt rateven di froy, for ahintsu.

00:19:26.952 --> 00:19:28.498
bin ikh geforn aleyn.

00:19:28.808 --> 00:19:30.219
vos hob ikh gezukht?

00:19:30.833 --> 00:19:31.890
kh'hob gezukht

00:19:32.655 --> 00:19:34.151
folgn di muter

00:19:34.545 --> 00:19:38.859
un tun dos vos zi hot gezogt, az zi git avek dray poshete ⟨far⟩ eyn gelerntn.

00:19:39.658 --> 00:19:42.068
kh'hob gefunen a gute shule, TACHKEMONI

00:19:42.068 --> 00:19:43.888
dos iz a tsionistishe shule.

00:19:44.147 --> 00:19:46.031
kh'hob gezen dortn az s'iz

00:19:46.746 --> 00:19:49.676
sheyn, un di kinder zenen oyfgetsoygn

00:19:50.897 --> 00:19:54.261
hob ikh geredt dortn, hob ikh shoyn gefunen di shule, hob ikh ongeshribn

00:19:54.261 --> 00:19:56.308
di froy az ikh hob a shule

00:19:57.175 --> 00:20:00.021
arbet papirn veln mir zen, nor di shule hob ikh.

00:20:00.364 --> 00:20:01.590
kh'hob fardint gelt

00:20:02.710 --> 00:20:03.818
in shvarts.

00:20:04.363 --> 00:20:05.977
ikh hob geshikt kartuzn

00:20:06.118 --> 00:20:09.385
keyn KIRYAT YAM. kh'hob zey gebrakht ahertsu

00:20:09.645 --> 00:20:11.782
hobn di frume gezukht a beker

00:20:12.058 --> 00:20:14.144
un ikh bin keyn mol nisht geven keyn beker

00:20:15.265 --> 00:20:17.351
hob ikh gezogt ikh bin a beker.

00:20:18.454 --> 00:20:20.164
ikh for in a kolonye

00:20:20.164 --> 00:20:21.494
a yidishe kolonye.

00:20:21.494 --> 00:20:23.664
kh'hob bay nakht ayngehitst dem oyvn

00:20:23.664 --> 00:20:28.484
kh'hob oysprubirt vi azoy me farkneytsht, ⟨iz⟩ di mame fleg kneytshn mit di hent, UNK a mashin.

00:20:28.697 --> 00:20:30.969
ikh hob azoy gebakn UNK bin avek.

00:20:32.157 --> 00:20:33.788
kh'hob fardint gelt dortn

00:20:34.654 --> 00:20:35.947
bin gekumen tsurik.

00:20:38.299 --> 00:20:39.828
d- di kinder hobn shoyn gelernt.

00:20:41.961 --> 00:20:43.912
tsvey yor hob ikh nisht gehat keyn papirn

00:20:45.927 --> 00:20:47.071
hot tsugeshikt

00:20:47.071 --> 00:20:48.210
der eybershter

00:20:48.210 --> 00:20:49.296
a ZUSKIND

00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:53.244
vos er hot a tsutrit tsu di regirung

00:20:53.537 --> 00:20:56.037
un er hot geven f- er hot gegebn

00:20:56.037 --> 00:20:59.277
far UNK layt, UNK

00:20:59.359 --> 00:21:00.990
un er hot undz ibergelozt.

00:21:02.329 --> 00:21:04.078
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu arbetn.

00:21:04.354 --> 00:21:06.103
kh'hob genumen lerers.

00:21:06.160 --> 00:21:08.111
di mame iz geshtanen far di oygn

00:21:12.083 --> 00:21:13.877
un ikh hob gezogt di froy

00:21:13.877 --> 00:21:15.181
"oyb mir ⟨veln⟩ nisht

00:21:15.205 --> 00:21:18.186
nemen lerers private, vet gornisht aroys."

00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:21.015
"vos vilstu makhn profesor fun zey?" zog ikh "neyn.

00:21:21.015 --> 00:21:22.337
ikh vil

00:21:23.085 --> 00:21:26.533
vet es geyn, vet es nisht geyn, nor prubirn darf men."

00:21:26.533 --> 00:21:29.283
di kinder hobn geendikt tsvelef klasn

00:21:29.283 --> 00:21:31.813
⟨MATURITET⟩ gemakht, TACHKEMONI

00:21:32.383 --> 00:21:34.267
un ikh hob zey arayngegebn in universitet.

00:21:35.809 --> 00:21:37.220
der kleyner zun

00:21:38.070 --> 00:21:41.068
hot gelernt az der k- dekan hot gezogt

00:21:41.192 --> 00:21:43.919
er farshteyt nisht vi azoy fun Rusland a kind

00:21:44.702 --> 00:21:46.282
ken azoy lernen.

00:21:47.959 --> 00:21:50.579
er hot geendikt, hob ikh gezogt "ALEX

00:21:50.579 --> 00:21:52.599
du host geendikt dem universitet. dos s'iz gornisht.

00:21:52.599 --> 00:21:55.089
me boyt a shtub, darf men mebl oykh hobn.

00:21:55.620 --> 00:21:57.824
hot er gemakht nokh a yor in England

00:21:58.472 --> 00:22:00.288
BUSINESS ADMINISTRATION

00:22:01.797 --> 00:22:05.959
un khasene gehat, gebrakht fun Rusland a froy.

00:22:06.657 --> 00:22:08.439
beyde hobn rusishe froyen.

00:22:08.968 --> 00:22:11.814
far vos? vayl zey hobn gelernt mit studentn

00:22:12.192 --> 00:22:15.139
un ikh hob UNK yinglekh ken men nemen shikses.

00:22:15.212 --> 00:22:17.619
efsher di shikses zenen nisht azoy shreklekh

00:22:18.351 --> 00:22:20.049
nor in Antverpn

00:22:20.848 --> 00:22:23.457
un biklal ikh hob gevolt yidishe kinder.

00:22:25.523 --> 00:22:27.949
kh'hob zey khasene gemakht. zey hobn kinder.

00:22:27.949 --> 00:22:29.701
ikh bin zeyer tsufridn

00:22:30.012 --> 00:22:31.390
vayl ikh hob gezogt

00:22:32.155 --> 00:22:33.516
az in lebn

00:22:33.876 --> 00:22:38.510
azoy vi ikh'l hobn vos tsu esn vel ikh zayn tsufridn. hob ikh azoy fri, bin ikh biklal tsufridn.

00:22:39.073 --> 00:22:40.091
far dem

00:22:40.091 --> 00:22:41.787
hob ikh nisht gekukt oyf gornisht.

00:22:41.787 --> 00:22:44.433
kh'hob geforn in ERETS. kh'hob gevust az ikh'l gornisht gefinen

00:22:44.743 --> 00:22:47.437
vayl SPIELBERG hot mir nisht geentfert

00:22:47.832 --> 00:22:49.226
nor ikh hob gezogt

00:22:49.502 --> 00:22:51.234
danken got

00:22:51.443 --> 00:22:53.141
vos aza mentsh

00:22:53.350 --> 00:22:54.677
hot zikh oyfgehoybn

00:22:55.307 --> 00:22:57.106
un gemakht aza film

00:22:58.159 --> 00:22:59.317
vos di velt

00:23:00.488 --> 00:23:01.916
iz ibergerasht.

00:23:02.614 --> 00:23:04.729
vos m'hot geshribn iz gornisht.

00:23:04.729 --> 00:23:06.844
s'iz go- s'iz epes, nor dos

00:23:07.626 --> 00:23:09.746
hot di velt geshtelt

00:23:10.714 --> 00:23:12.952
az s'iz nokh do aza mentsh

00:23:13.110 --> 00:23:14.499
